<h2>Aspect Cabinetry</h2>

<div class="module-section">
  <h3>Construction</h3>
  <p>Aspect is the value-tier offering in the WW Wood Products portfolio. It provides solid cabinetry with select finish and door style options at a more accessible price point — ideal for rental properties, budget-conscious renovations, or entry-level new construction.</p>
</div>

<div class="module-section">
  <h3>Key Details</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Streamlined door and finish selection for faster ordering</li>
    <li>5-year warranty</li>
    <li>Shorter lead times than Shiloh/Eclipse</li>
    <li>Strong option when budget is the primary driver</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<h2>Pronorm German Kitchens</h2>

<div class="module-section">
  <h3>Overview</h3>
  <p>Pronorm is a premium fitted German kitchen brand manufactured in Vlotho, Germany since 1945. Available in the US exclusively through Pinnacle Sales dealers. Three product lines (Y-Line, X-Line, Proline128) can be freely combined on a universal platform. Over 100 door finishes, 610mm (24″) American-depth base and tall cabinets, and construction details that set it apart from both domestic and imported competitors.</p>
</div>

<div class="module-section">
  <h3>Key Differentiators</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>610mm (24″) base and tall cabinet depths — fits American kitchens without compromise</li>
    <li>ProTech X premium drawer system: 60kg soft-close capacity, no visible screws</li>
    <li>Organic glass doors: anti-fingerprint, scratch-resistant, hygienic</li>
    <li>Climate-neutral since 2021, PEFC certified, "Furniture Made in Germany" mark</li>
    <li>Fills the gap between entry-level German brands and ultra-premium (SieMatic, Poggenpohl)</li>
    <li>Typical installations: $40,000–$150,000+</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<h2>Vistora Closets</h2>

<div class="module-section">
  <h3>Overview</h3>
  <p>Vistora is a fully assembled modular closet system built by W.W. Wood Products in Dudley, Missouri. Where typical closet systems require 20-30 individual parts per closet, Vistora uses 4-5 pre-assembled floor-mounted modules with accessories already built in. Nine finish options. Hardware in Matte Black and Matte Chrome. Ideal add-on for kitchen dealers who want to capture whole-home projects.</p>
</div>

